    <title>利用hexo和github搭建个人博客</title>
    <url>/2020/09/23/%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8hexo%E5%92%8Cgithub%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-安装Git"><a href="#1-安装Git" class="headerlink" title="1.安装Git"></a>1.安装Git</h2><h3 id="1-1下载网址"><a href="#1-1下载网址" class="headerlink" title="1.1下载网址"></a>1.1下载网址</h3><p><a href="https://git-scm.com/">https://git-scm.com/</a></p>
<h3 id="1-2配置环境变量"><a href="#1-2配置环境变量" class="headerlink" title="1.2配置环境变量"></a>1.2配置环境变量</h3><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">D:\Git\cmd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="1-3查看安装版本"><a href="#1-3查看安装版本" class="headerlink" title="1.3查看安装版本"></a>1.3查看安装版本</h3><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git -<span class="literal">-version</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="1-4新建github公共仓库"><a href="#1-4新建github公共仓库" class="headerlink" title="1.4新建github公共仓库"></a>1.4新建github公共仓库</h3><p><img src="/2020/09/23/%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8hexo%E5%92%8Cgithub%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image-20200923212039549.png" alt="image-20200923212039549"></p>
<h3 id="1-5配置github用户名和邮箱"><a href="#1-5配置github用户名和邮箱" class="headerlink" title="1.5配置github用户名和邮箱"></a>1.5配置github用户名和邮箱</h3><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config -<span class="literal">-global</span> user.name <span class="string">&quot;username&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">git config -<span class="literal">-global</span> user.email <span class="string">&quot;email&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看全局的用户名和邮箱</span></span><br><span class="line">git config -<span class="literal">-global</span> user.name </span><br><span class="line">git config -<span class="literal">-global</span> user.email</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="1-6生成ssh密钥"><a href="#1-6生成ssh密钥" class="headerlink" title="1.6生成ssh密钥"></a>1.6生成ssh密钥</h3><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh<span class="literal">-keygen</span> <span class="literal">-t</span> rsa 或 ssh<span class="literal">-keygen</span> <span class="literal">-t</span> rsa <span class="literal">-C</span> <span class="string">&quot;xxx@foxmail.com&quot;</span>  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 连敲三次回车键，然后C:\Users\你的用户名.ssh目录下会生成 id_sra.pub,复制里面的内容</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="/2020/09/23/%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8hexo%E5%92%8Cgithub%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image-20200923213011220.png" alt="image-20200923213011220"></p>
<h2 id="2安装Node-js"><a href="#2安装Node-js" class="headerlink" title="2安装Node.js"></a>2安装Node.js</h2><h3 id="2-1下载网址"><a href="#2-1下载网址" class="headerlink" title="2.1下载网址:"></a>2.1下载网址:</h3><p> <a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/">https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/</a></p>
<h3 id="2-2修该全模块和缓存所在路径"><a href="#2-2修该全模块和缓存所在路径" class="headerlink" title="2.2修该全模块和缓存所在路径"></a>2.2修该全模块和缓存所在路径</h3><p>在Node.js安装目录下新建node_global和node_cache目录，然后在控制台输入：</p>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config <span class="built_in">set</span> prefix <span class="string">&quot;D:\Nodejs\node_global&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">npm config <span class="built_in">set</span> cache <span class="string">&quot;D:\Nodejs\node_cache&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="2-3配置环境变量"><a href="#2-3配置环境变量" class="headerlink" title="2.3配置环境变量"></a>2.3配置环境变量</h3><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">D:\Nodejs\</span><br><span class="line">D:\Nodejs\node_global</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="2-4查看安装版本"><a href="#2-4查看安装版本" class="headerlink" title="2.4查看安装版本"></a>2.4查看安装版本</h3><p>控制台输入<code>node -v</code>或 <code>node --version</code></p>
<h3 id="2-5添加淘宝镜像"><a href="#2-5添加淘宝镜像" class="headerlink" title="2.5添加淘宝镜像"></a>2.5添加淘宝镜像</h3><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 1.临时使用</span></span><br><span class="line">npm -<span class="literal">-registry</span> https://registry.npm.taobao.org install express</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 2.持久使用（推荐）</span></span><br><span class="line">npm config <span class="built_in">set</span> registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 配置后可通过使用下面方式来验证是否成功</span></span><br><span class="line">npm config get registry</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 然后通过npm命令来安装express</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install express</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 3.通过cnpm使用</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install <span class="literal">-g</span> cnpm -<span class="literal">-registry</span>=https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 然后可使用cnpm命令来安装express</span></span><br><span class="line">cnpm install express</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="3-安装Hexo"><a href="#3-安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="3.安装Hexo"></a>3.安装Hexo</h2><h3 id="3-1使用Node-js安装hexo脚手架"><a href="#3-1使用Node-js安装hexo脚手架" class="headerlink" title="3.1使用Node.js安装hexo脚手架"></a>3.1使用Node.js安装hexo脚手架</h3><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo<span class="literal">-cli</span> <span class="literal">-g</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-2查看hexo版本"><a href="#3-2查看hexo版本" class="headerlink" title="3.2查看hexo版本"></a>3.2查看hexo版本</h3><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo version 或 hexo <span class="literal">-v</span> 或 hexo -<span class="literal">-version</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-3初始化项目myhexo"><a href="#3-3初始化项目myhexo" class="headerlink" title="3.3初始化项目myhexo"></a>3.3初始化项目myhexo</h3><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 在当前目录下生成myhexo目录</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo init myhexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-4启动hexo服务"><a href="#3-4启动hexo服务" class="headerlink" title="3.4启动hexo服务"></a>3.4启动hexo服务</h3><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo server 或 hexo s</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># http://localhost:4000 Ctrl+C停止服务</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-5配置myhexo目录下的-config-yml文件"><a href="#3-5配置myhexo目录下的-config-yml文件" class="headerlink" title="3.5配置myhexo目录下的_config.yml文件"></a>3.5配置myhexo目录下的_config.yml文件</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">git@github.com:fanyinhang/fanyinhang.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-6安装hexo-deployer-git"><a href="#3-6安装hexo-deployer-git" class="headerlink" title="3.6安装hexo-deployer-git"></a>3.6安装hexo-deployer-git</h3><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo<span class="literal">-deployer</span><span class="literal">-git</span> -<span class="literal">-save</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-7生成md文件"><a href="#3-7生成md文件" class="headerlink" title="3.7生成md文件"></a>3.7生成md文件</h3><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># myhexo\source\_posts\test.md</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo n test 或 hexo new test</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-8生成静态网页"><a href="#3-8生成静态网页" class="headerlink" title="3.8生成静态网页"></a>3.8生成静态网页</h3><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo gererate 或 hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-9将hexo部署到github"><a href="#3-9将hexo部署到github" class="headerlink" title="3.9将hexo部署到github"></a>3.9将hexo部署到github</h3><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo deployer 或 hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-10更换hexo默认主题"><a href="#3-10更换hexo默认主题" class="headerlink" title="3.10更换hexo默认主题"></a>3.10更换hexo默认主题</h3><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone git@github.com:shashankmehta/greyshade.git .themes/greyshade</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 修改_config.yaml文件</span></span><br><span class="line">theme: greyshade</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate 或 hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo deployer 或 hexo d</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 访问fanyinhang.github.io</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-11图片上传"><a href="#3-11图片上传" class="headerlink" title="3.11图片上传"></a>3.11图片上传</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 安装图片插件</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-asset-image --save</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 修改_config.yaml文件</span><br><span class="line">post_asset_folder: true</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 此时使用hexo n test会在myhexo目录下生成test.md和test目录</span><br><span class="line">hexo n test</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-12使用Typora编写md文件"><a href="#3-12使用Typora编写md文件" class="headerlink" title="3.12使用Typora编写md文件"></a>3.12使用Typora编写md文件</h3><p><img src="/2020/09/23/%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8hexo%E5%92%8Cgithub%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image-20200923220108041.png" alt="image-20200923220108041"></p>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 此时插入的图片会自动放在test目录下</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
